quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,La uksimu biyevmilkÄḟyameti
  75,2,Ve la uksimu binnefsillevvameti
  75,3,EyahsebulÂṀinsanu ellen necmeÂṀa ÂṀÄḟzamehu
  75,4,Bela kadiriyne ÂṀala en nusevviye benanehu
  75,5,Bel yuriydulÂṀinsanu liyefcure emamehu
  75,6,YesÂṀelu eyyane yevmulkÄḟyameti
  75,7,Feiza berikalbesaru
  75,8,Ve hasefelkameru
  75,9,Ve cumiÂṀaÅÅemsu velkameru
  75,10,YekululÂṀinsanu yevmeizin eynelmeferru
  75,11,Kella la vezere
  75,12,ÄḞla rabbike yevmeizinilmustekarru
  75,13,YunebbeulÂṀinsanu yevmeizin bima kaddeme ve ahha re
  75,14,BelilÂṀinsanu ÂṀala nefsihi besÄḟyretun
  75,15,Ve lev elka meÂṀaziyrehu
  75,16,La tuharrik bihi lisaneke litaÂṀcele bihi
  75,17,ÄḞnneÂṀaleyna cemÂṀahu ve kurÂṀanehu
  75,18,Feiza kareÂṀnahu fettebÄḟÂṀkurÂṀanehu
  75,19,Summe inne ÂṀaleyna beyanehu
  75,20,Kella bel tuhÄḟbbunelÂṀacilete
  75,21,Ve tezerunelÂṀahÄḟrete
  75,22,Vucuhun yevmeizin nadÄḟretun
  75,23,ÄḞla rabbiha nazÄḟretun
  75,24,Ve vucuhun yevmeizin basireÂṀun
  75,25,Tezunnu en yufÂṀale biha fakÄḟretun
  75,26,Kella iza beleÄatitterakÄḟye
  75,27,Ve kÄḟyle men rakÄḟn
  75,28,Ve zanne ennehulfraku
  75,29,Velteffetissaku bissakÄḟ
  75,30,ÄḞla rabbike yevmeizinilmesaku